Explore the controversial concept of Project Blue Beam, alleged to be a plan to hoax a threat from outer space to unite humanity, akin to themes seen in movies like Independence Day. Delve into the intrigue surrounding UFO narratives and historical events, including insights into early UFO abductions and President Obama's involvement in documenting these stories.

Dr. Steven Greer returns for a second sit-down with Patrick Bet-David, and you won't want to miss it! This episode of the PBD podcast features one of the wildest conversations yet, covering government conspiracies, whistleblowers, aliens, secret patents, teleportation, Nikola Tesla, and more. Tune in for an unforgettable discussion!

